    <br>
<p>Specifies the optional InfluxDB format/precision (rfc3339/h/m/s/ms/u) of the timestamp of the measurements and weather data: rfc3339 (YYYY-MM-DDTHH:MM:SS.nnnnnnnnnZ), h (hours), m (minutes), s (seconds), ms (milliseconds), u (microseconds). Precision defaults to rfc3339. Example: <code>rfc3339</code></p>
        </div>
